## tenacitas/builders ##
Under `tenacitas/builders` we have:

    .
    └── qtcreator
So, for now, there is only a build system based on [QtCreator](https://www.qt.io/). 
Inside `tenacitas/builder/qtcreator` there is:

    .
    ├── common.pri
    ├── concurrent
    ├── logger

`common.pri` is a file with definitions common to build all the components.
In `tenacitas/builders/qtcreator/logger` we have files and directories to be used by [QtCreator](https://www.qt.io/) in order to build **tenacitas.logger**:

