## Building the library ##
Start [QtCreator](https://www.qt.io/), open the `tenacitas/builders/qtcreator/logger/logger.pro` project file, and read the instructions in [QtCreator README.md](../../builders/qtcreator/README.md)

# Using the library #
The files `tenacitas/code/logger/cerr.h`, `tenacitas/code/logger/cout.h` and `tenacitas/code/logger/file.h` are all the header files you need, plus the ```tenacitas.logger.so``` library file. You will need to include the ```.../tenacitas/code``` to your compiler include path.

**Enjoy!**
